The paper discusses the use of data mining techniques to extract useful knowledge from web content, which is closely related to information retrieval (cs.IR) and natural language processing (cs.CL). The paper also mentions the use of image analysis tools, which falls under computer vision (cs.CV). Additionally, the paper discusses the organization and categorization of web content, which is related to database systems (cs.DB) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI).
